<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CoBeachs | Relaxed Beachside Café</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap 5 CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;1,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --sunset-orange: #ff8c42;
            --sunset-dark: #e07a5f;
            --dark-purple: #2d132c;
            --header-purple: #190918;
            --ocean-black: #0d0d0d;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ff8c42, #f96d00, #2d132c);
            background-attachment: fixed;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: var(--header-purple) !important;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--sunset-orange);
        }

        .hero-banner {
            background-color: var(--dark-purple);
            padding: 100px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 50% 20px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 50% 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        .hero-banner h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: var(--sunset-orange);
        }

        .menu-section {
            padding: 80px 0;
        }

        .category-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--sunset-orange);
            display: inline-block;
            width: auto;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .menu-card {
            background: rgba(25, 9, 24, 0.85);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 140, 66, 0.3);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .menu-card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
            border-color: var(--sunset-orange);
        }

        .placeholder-img {
            width: 150px;
            min-width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            background: #333;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #666;
            font-style: italic;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .btn-black {
            background-color: var(--ocean-black);
            color: white;
            border: 1px solid var(--sunset-orange);
            padding: 10px 25px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-black:hover {
            background-color: var(--sunset-orange);
            color: var(--ocean-black);
        }

        .hours-box {
            background: rgba(13, 13, 13, 0.7);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px dashed var(--sunset-orange);
        }

        .contact-section {
            background-color: var(--header-purple);
            padding: 60px 20px;
            border-radius: 30px 30px 0 0;
        }

        .form-control {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border: 1px solid #444;
            color: white;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #000;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #888;
        }

        /* AI Features Styling */
        .ai-suggestion-box {
            background: rgba(255, 140, 66, 0.1);
            border: 2px solid var(--sunset-orange);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: none;
        }

        .loading-spinner {
            display: none;
            width: 2rem;
            height: 2rem;
            border: 0.25em solid currentColor;
            border-right-color: transparent;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: spinner-border .75s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes spinner-border {
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .menu-card {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }
            .placeholder-img {
                width: 100%;
                height: 120px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark sticky-top">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold" href="#" style="color: var(--sunset-orange); letter-spacing: 2px;">CoBeachs</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#menu">Menu</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#hours">Waktu Operasi</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#contact">Hubungi Kami</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Banner -->
    <header class="hero-banner">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>CoBeachs</h1>
            <p class="lead">Nikmati suasana matahari terbenam dengan secawan kebahagiaan.</p>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-2 mt-3 flex-wrap">
                <a href="#menu" class="btn btn-black">Lihat Menu</a>
                <button onclick="speakWelcome()" class="btn btn-black">✨ Dengar Aluan</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- AI Suggestion Section -->
    <section class="container mt-5">
        <div class="card bg-dark border-secondary p-4 text-center">
            <h3>✨ Cadangkan Menu Berdasarkan Mood</h3>
            <p>Beritahu kami bagaimana perasaan anda hari ini, dan AI kami akan mencadangkan hidangan terbaik!</p>
            <div class="input-group mb-3">
                <input type="text" id="userMood" class="form-control" placeholder="Contoh: Saya rasa penat tapi lapar...">
                <button class="btn btn-black" type="button" onclick="generateAiSuggestion()">✨ Cari Menu</button>
            </div>
            <div id="aiLoader" class="loading-spinner mx-auto mb-3"></div>
            <div id="suggestionOutput" class="ai-suggestion-box text-start"></div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Menu Section -->
    <section id="menu" class="container menu-section">
        <!-- Hidangan Utama -->
        <div class="text-center">
            <h2 class="category-title">Hidangan Utama</h2>
        </div>
        <div id="meals-list" class="row">
            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="card menu-card">
                    <div class="placeholder-img">[Imej Salmon Panggang]</div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5>Sunset Grilled Salmon</h5>
                        <p class="small text-light-emphasis">Dipanggang dengan parutan kulit oren dan herba segar.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card menu-card">
                    <div class="placeholder-img">[Imej Burger Tropikal]</div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5>Tropical Beach Burger</h5>
                        <p class="small text-light-emphasis">Patty daging lembu dengan nanas panggang yang juicy.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card menu-card">
                    <div class="placeholder-img">[Imej Seafood Paella]</div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5>Seafood Paella</h5>
                        <p class="small text-light-emphasis">Hasil laut segar dihidangkan bersama nasi safron.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Minuman -->
        <div class="text-center mt-5">
            <h2 class="category-title">Minuman Segar</h2>
        </div>
        <div id="drinks-list" class="row">
            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="card menu-card">
                    <div class="placeholder-img">[Imej Mojito]</div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5>Classic Mojito</h5>
                        <p class="small text-light-emphasis">Pudina segar, limau nipis, dan soda yang menyegarkan.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card menu-card">
                    <div class="placeholder-img">[Imej Mocktail]</div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5>Sunset Mocktail</h5>
                        <p class="small text-light-emphasis">Campuran grenadine, oren, dan nanas.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card menu-card">
                    <div class="placeholder-img">[Imej Coconut Latte]</div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5>Iced Coconut Latte</h5>
                        <p class="small text-light-emphasis">Kopi espresso bersama santan kelapa berkrim.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Pencuci Mulut -->
        <div class="text-center mt-5">
            <h2 class="category-title">Pencuci Mulut</h2>
        </div>
        <div id="desserts-list" class="row">
            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="card menu-card">
                    <div class="placeholder-img">[Imej Pulut Mangga]</div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5>Mango Sticky Rice</h5>
                        <p class="small text-light-emphasis">Mangga manis bersama pulut dan santan pekat.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card menu-card">
                    <div class="placeholder-img">[Imej Kek Coklat Lava]</div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5>Chocolate Lava Cake</h5>
                        <p class="small text-light-emphasis">Dihidangkan panas bersama gelato vanila.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card menu-card">
                    <div class="placeholder-img">[Imej Tart Limau]</div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5>Key Lime Tart</h5>
                        <p class="small text-light-emphasis">Tart limau masam manis dengan kerak biskut rangup.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Operational Hours -->
    <section id="hours" class="container py-5">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="hours-box">
                    <h2 class="mb-3">Waktu Operasi</h2>
                    <p class="fs-4 fw-light">Setiap Hari</p>
                    <p class="display-6 fw-bold" style="color: var(--sunset-orange);">4 PM - 12 AM</p>
                    <p class="mt-3 text-secondary">Sertai kami untuk pemandangan 'Golden Hour' yang terbaik.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact & Feedback -->
    <section id="contact" class="contact-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-5 mb-5">
                    <h2 class="mb-4" style="color: var(--sunset-orange);">Hubungi Kami</h2>
                    <p>Kami ingin mendengar pengalaman anda di CoBeachs. Sebarang cadangan amat dialu-alukan.</p>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled mt-4">
                        <li class="mb-2">📍 Sunset Beach, North Coast</li>
                        <li class="mb-2">📞 +60 12-345 6789</li>
                        <li class="mb-2">📧 hello@cobeachs.com</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-7">
                    <div class="card border-0 p-4" style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);">
                        <form>
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                    <label class="form-label">Nama</label>
                                    <input type="text" id="contactName" class="form-control" placeholder="Nama Anda">
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                    <label class="form-label">Email</label>
                                    <input type="email" id="contactEmail" class="form-control" placeholder="nama@email.com">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label class="form-label">Maklum Balas</label>
                                <textarea class="form-control" id="contactMessage" rows="4" placeholder="Tulis sesuatu di sini..."></textarea>
                            </div>
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-black w-100" onclick="analyzeFeedback()">Hantar Mesej & ✨ Analisis Sentimen</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="text-center">
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2024 CoBeachs Beachside Café. Hak Cipta Terpelihara.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
